HEADWORD: Smokestack
<hw>Smoke"stack`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A chimney; esp.,
a pipe serving as a chimney, as the pipe which carries off the smoke of
a locomotive, the funnel of a steam vessel, etc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

